[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] Reports an error identified by `$message` if the file specified by `$expectedFile` does not have `$actualString` as its contents.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] `assertStringNotEqualsFile()` is the inverse of this assertion and takes the same arguments.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] Reports an error identified by `$message` if the value of `$actual` is not valid JSON.
