[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] `assertJsonFileNotEqualsJsonFile()` is the inverse of this assertion and takes the same arguments.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] Reports an error identified by `$message` if the value of `$actualJson` does not match the value of `$expectedFile`.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] `assertJsonStringNotEqualsJsonFile()` is the inverse of this assertion and takes the same arguments.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] Reports an error identified by `$message` if the value of `$actualJson` does not match the value of `$expectedJson`.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] `assertJsonStringNotEqualsJsonString()` is the inverse of this assertion and takes the same arguments.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] Reports an error identified by `$message` if the XML document in `$actualFile` is not equal to the XML document in `$expectedFile`.
[src:phpunit/assertions-p03] `assertXmlFileNotEqualsXmlFile()` is the inverse of this assertion and takes the same arguments.
